  m_text: "Monotrum (\uBAA8\uB178\uD2B8\uB7FC / \u30E2\u30CE\u30C8\u30E9\u30E0) \r\n--------------------\r\nMade
    with UnityEngine\r\n--------------------\r\nCharacter Asset\r\nUnity-Chan (\u30E6\u30CB\u30C6\u30A3\u3061\u3083\u3093
    Sunny Side Up)\r\n\xA9 Unity Technologies Japan/UCL\r\n--------------------\r\nAudio
    \r\n- Neon nights - Patrick Patrikios\r\n- Make You Move - Ofshane\r\n- Glaze
    My Ego - The Soundlings\r\n- Exploring The Crystal Caves - Asher Fulero\r\n-
    Anywhen You Say - Cheel\r\nfrom YouTube Studio Audio Library\r\n--------------------\r\nUsed
    Font - SIL Open Font License\r\nGoogle Noto Sans, OpenSans, Audiowide\r\n--------------------\r\nUnityAssets\r\n-
    Modern UI Pack\r\n- Beautify 3 - Advanced Post Processing\r\n- Starter Assets
    - ThirdPerson\r\n- MagicaCloth2\r\n- Grid Master (Texture Use)\r\n--------------------"
